To run the main program, just run the python file "wc.py" with the text file that you want to analyze.
command example: "python3 wc.py ./text". For the feature of replacement, you need to provide a existing word and also the new word you want to replace with.



To run the unit test, run the python file "stats.py", when testing on replacement, you need to provide a existing word and also the new word you want to replace with.

